Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:54.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(598,464)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.86,0:00:59.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班十八小时的痛苦终于结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:59.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,End of another 18-hour shift of misery
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.33,0:01:01.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:01.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy there
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what are you two laddies
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.54,0:01:06.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这周末有什么计划
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:06.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have planned for this weekend?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.29,0:01:08.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要给小蜗的壳做抛光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:08.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm polishing Gary's shell
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.38,0:01:18.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要参加一场后后前现代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:18.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going to a post-post-pre-modern
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.93,0:01:22.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非构成派舞蹈表演
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:22.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,unconstructivist dance performance
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.98,0:01:28.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:28.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's uh
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.31,0:01:29.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:29.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fascinating
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.32,0:01:32.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不必做那堆无聊事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:32.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Instead of that malarkey
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.98,0:01:36.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们想不想周末登上我的全新游艇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:36.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what would you say to a leisurely weekend sailing trip
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.53,0:01:38.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来场航海旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:38.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on me brand-new yacht
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.95,0:01:41.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阳光照在你脸上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:41.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sun in your face
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.91,0:01:47.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清风吹在你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:47.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The wind in your, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.50,0:01:49.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抬头纹上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:49.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,head wrinkles
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.34,0:01:56.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒可以来一场轻松愉快的航海旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:56.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I wouldn't mind a nice relaxing ocean cruise
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.84,0:01:57.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:57.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.84,0:02:00.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天一大早码头见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:00.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll see you at the dock bright and early tomorrow morning
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.14,0:02:03.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}第二天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:04.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(584,692)}酷乐湖\N沙丘 码头
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.69,0:02:12.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我已经打扮齐全准备好要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:12.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I'm all dressed up and ready to
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.02,0:02:14.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,潜泳了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:14.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,snorkel
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.40,0:02:16.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:16.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a second
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.11,0:02:17.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:17.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.78,0:02:18.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:18.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's your ship?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有种可疑的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something smells fishy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.66,0:02:23.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可别让后桅弯曲变形了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:23.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't get your mizzenmast in a twist
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:27.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(542,820)}游艇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:27.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(544,218)}实木 组装\N涂料 展示
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.79,0:02:25.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要的船就在这
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:25.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got your ship right here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要一点组装
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some assembly required
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.79,0:02:33.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须自己把船组装起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:33.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to build the ship
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.13,0:02:36.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能自己把船组装起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:36.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We get to build the ship
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,旱鸭子才坐预制的船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Premade vessels are for land-lubbers
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.93,0:02:41.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真正的水手都自己造船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:41.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Real sailors build their own ships
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在快去干活  你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get to work, you two
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.51,0:02:45.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,作为一名老海军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:45.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And as an old navy man
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.64,0:02:48.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就来负责最难的那部分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:48.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be responsible for the most difficult part
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敢问最难的部分是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that would be
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.15,0:02:52.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在旁边监督
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:52.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Supervising
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:57.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1558,620)}豪船杂志
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老海军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old navy man
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.36,0:03:04.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老懒鬼还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:04.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More like old lazy man
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  来把事成了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get this over with
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.54,0:03:12.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说明书在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:12.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now where are the instructions?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来找
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll find them
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.25,0:03:15.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说明书  说明书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:15.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Instructions, instructions
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如何组装
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How to assemble
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.46,0:03:19.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:19.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got them
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.68,0:03:21.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:21.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step one
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.10,0:03:25.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:25.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.06,0:03:34.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我们该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:34.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.06,0:03:35.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别担心  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:35.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.65,0:03:38.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道要怎么处理这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:38.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know exactly how to handle this situation
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.86,0:03:39.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:39.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.69,0:03:42.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要跟随内心  凭感觉走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:42.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We just need to follow our hearts
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.00,0:03:53.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  第一块完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:53.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, I did the first piece
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你这傻蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you clam head
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.96,0:03:58.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能先安桅杆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:58.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't put up the mast first
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.42,0:04:00.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说什么  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:00.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.38,0:04:01.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:01.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.80,0:04:03.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你这傻蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:03.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you clam head
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.35,0:04:14.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须先从骨架装起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:14.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have to start with the frame
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.31,0:04:19.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  把它弯成船形
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:19.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, now bend it into a boat shape
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挠挠挠挠挠挠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tickle, tickle, tickle
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.58,0:04:33.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  木板不是用来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:33.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, wood planks are not
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挠的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ticklish
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.42,0:04:45.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}尝试组装骨架很多次之后
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,建成了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来握个手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put her there
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.22,0:04:51.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:51.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.20,0:05:09.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你到底是在搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:09.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in the name of all that's salty are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是在浪费贵得要命的木材
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're wasting expensive lumber
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.95,0:05:15.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们这是在给船组装骨架  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:15.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're trying to build the ship's frame, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,组装骨架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Building the frame?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:22.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1366,270)}预制船骨架
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.42,0:05:22.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,骨架早都给你准备好一份了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:22.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They give you one all ready to go
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看一看  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a gander, boyo
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我状态良好  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm shipshape, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(853.333,918)}成了船的形状
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回去干活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快要退潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The tide's going out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:48.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,876)}钉子
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,死也钉不下去是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A stubborn one, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有看到过一座锚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you see an anchor?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我锚好像掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I dropped one
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然交换位置行不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't we switch places?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.20,0:06:39.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这下面干活  我在那上面干活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:39.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You work down here and I'll work up there
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安全多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Much safer
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不在白痴底下干活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never work below an idiot
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心上面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out above
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.63,0:06:48.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:48.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Above?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:07:00.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1510,654)}章鱼哥
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.73,0:07:01.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:01.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在上面有看到过一座保险箱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a safe up here?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我保险箱好像掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I dropped it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.53,0:07:11.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从现在起你就到我旁边干活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:11.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From now on you're working next to me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.28,0:07:14.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方便我盯着你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:14.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where I can keep an eye on you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.28,0:07:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可太棒了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's so sweet, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.12,0:07:21.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}尝试组装游艇更多次之后
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.71,0:07:28.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的船组装好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:28.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your ship is finished
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.76,0:07:32.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,基本上长得像船的就当成船了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:32.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We use the term "ship" very loosely
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.31,0:07:38.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉有点不对头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:38.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's a little off the beam
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.94,0:07:41.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:41.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.64,0:07:44.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要再漆上去一层闪亮的涂料就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:44.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All she needs is a nice shiny coat of paint
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:56.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1282,218)}海洋秘方号
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.28,0:07:52.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海洋秘方号准备好启航了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:52.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The S.S. Sea-cret Formula is ready to set sail
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.78,0:07:55.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要拖进酷乐湖里就能开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:55.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as soon as you two drag her into the lagoon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:59.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1170,492)}救生员
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mush
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.27,0:08:23.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  至少这周末并没完全被浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:23.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least this weekend isn't a total waste
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.10,0:08:25.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先别急  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:25.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not so fast, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.31,0:08:27.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还有工作要做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:27.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You still have work to do
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:36.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(646,778)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.61,0:08:36.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临海上蟹堡王的盛大揭幕仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the grand opening
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:36.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of the Krusty Krab of the high seas
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里价格更高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and even higher prices
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.66,0:08:42.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想都别想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:42.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.16,0:08:44.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一步都不会从这地方挪开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:44.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am not moving from this spot
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.08,0:08:45.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:45.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:50.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(318,242)}菜单\N但是在船上
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好兴奋啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How exciting, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.63,0:08:55.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能一边翻肉饼一边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:55.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get to flip patties and be
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.34,0:08:58.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晕船了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:58.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,seasick at the same time
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.22,0:09:03.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱可不在酷乐湖上面卖什么吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:03.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not gonna sell any food in the middle of a lagoon
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.68,0:09:06.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来份蟹黄堡套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:06.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like one Krabby Patty combo
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.81,0:09:08.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面多加套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:08.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with extra combo on it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的餐好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your order
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,稍息  水手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At ease, sailor
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.21,0:10:11.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道酷乐湖有座小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:11.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't know there was an island in Goo Lagoon
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.26,0:10:19.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正前方有屁股山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:19.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Butt-burg, dead ahead
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人都抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone, hold fast
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:29.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1602,204)}竖笛资讯
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.52,0:10:35.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王的鼻毛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:35.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great Neptune's nose hair
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.63,0:10:56.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请来一份双层蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:56.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One double Krabby Patty, please
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:22.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1366,352)}酷乐湖
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.87,0:11:32.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把你们这所有蟹黄堡都给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:32.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me all the Krabby Patties you got, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.25,0:11:35.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经饿到都能去海之霸用餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:35.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry, I can eat at the Chum Bucket
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,甚至还能喜欢上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and like it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,告诉你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, I'll tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:43.51,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}墙中殿堂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:45.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(693.802,372)\frz28.71}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:45.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(711.802,668)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:49.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(639.802,460)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(759.802,668)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(723.802,540)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(571.802,546)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(659.802,540)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁想吃点心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who wants snackies?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快过来  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Gar-bear
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.27,0:12:00.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我保证过你数学得A的话会给你点心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:12:00.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promised you a treat if you got an A on your math test
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.74,0:12:03.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快过来  小蜗小蜗小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:03.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, snaily, snaily, snaily
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:04.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,582)}蜗牛点心
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.57,0:12:04.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在哪  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:04.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are you, boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.37,0:12:08.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:08.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.96,0:12:14.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:14.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.09,0:12:19.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:19.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.36,0:12:40.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,墙上突出来的那块一直都会喵喵叫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:40.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did that lump in my wall always meow?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.69,0:12:43.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你是怎么进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:43.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, how'd you get in there?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又要怎么救你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And how do I get you out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1164,922)}欢迎
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.80,0:13:06.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:06.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把自己反锁起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I locked myself in
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.81,0:13:17.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我到处找你找好久了  小先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:17.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been looking all over for you, little mister
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.03,0:13:26.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  好心的陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:26.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, kind stranger
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.96,0:13:43.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以叫我沃利C
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:43.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can call me Wally C
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:43.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1106,920)}墙 壁
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.05,0:13:45.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我就住在墙里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:45.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for in these walls I live
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我叫做海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, my name be SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.89,0:13:55.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我是块穿方裤子的海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:55.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for I'm a sponge who wear square pants
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.35,0:13:57.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是怎么进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:57.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you get in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Long ago
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.32,0:14:03.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是个杂务工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:03.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a handyman was I
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.40,0:14:05.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:05.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,till
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:07.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(984,706)}出售
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被永远关了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me eternal confinement
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那玩意正常吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that normal?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.21,0:14:26.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,房子一点小问题没啥大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:26.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's just the house settling
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.97,0:14:28.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成交
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:28.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sold
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.84,0:14:35.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是  我的命运被永远抛进了墙里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:35.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And thus, me fate was forever cast in drywall
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.56,0:14:37.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讲完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:37.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The end
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.14,0:14:39.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:39.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.94,0:14:43.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你居然一直都住在墙里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:43.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you've been living in the walls all this time
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.27,0:14:46.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许我们能一起找到办法出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:46.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can find a way out together
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.07,0:14:52.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凡进入这个被约束的世界就没有出口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:52.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There be no exit once ye enter this restrictive realm
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.16,0:14:54.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不想出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:54.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to get out of here?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nay
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.33,0:14:59.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,沃利已经不再关心外面的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:59.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wally no longer cares for the outside realm
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.75,0:15:03.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这  拥挤狭窄只是一种心态
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:03.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, feeling cramped be just a state of mind
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.47,0:15:17.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到墙中殿堂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:17.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wallhalla
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.18,0:15:21.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想不想来参观一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:21.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How would you like a grand tour?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.52,0:15:23.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们想参观参观
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:23.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We would love the grand tour
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.15,0:15:30.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临我的霉菌园
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:30.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to me mold garden
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的曲霉菌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me aspergillus
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去  去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shoo, shoo
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.29,0:15:40.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你花园里还种了葡萄干
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:40.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see you're also growing raisins in your garden
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,葡萄干
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Raisins?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.46,0:15:44.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些是海胆粪蛋子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:44.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those are urchin droppings
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.35,0:15:57.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,沃利  有个出口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:57.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wally, there's a way out
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.18,0:15:59.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:15:59.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nay
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.10,0:16:03.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只是我的魔法冰箱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:03.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's just me magic fridge
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:07.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1220,506)}嫩肚肚海草汁
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Magic?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管我吃多少喝多少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No matter how much I eat or drink
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.20,0:16:19.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰箱都会再变出来不少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:19.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,she always provideth more
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也有嫩肚肚海草汁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get tender tummy kelp juice, too
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.79,0:16:27.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过还得是魔法冰箱里的更好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:27.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure tastes better from the magic fridge, though
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.92,0:16:31.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,墙中殿堂还有不少神奇缝隙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:31.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There be many magical crannies in Wallhalla
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.68,0:16:38.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,墙中殿堂甚至还有魔法药柜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:38.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wallhalla even has a magic medicine cabinet
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.89,0:16:40.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在这放了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:40.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where I keep
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.81,0:16:44.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的魔法鼻刷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me magic nose brush
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刷刷鼻子里头的毛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brush the hairs within your nose
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.61,0:16:55.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样才不会掉衣服上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:55.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so they don't drip upon your clothes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,墙中殿堂太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wallhalla is amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.37,0:17:01.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,墙背后是个无忧无虑的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:01.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To think that right behind the wall
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.41,0:17:03.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想想就感觉很美好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:03.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is a world without problems
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.46,0:17:08.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,墙中殿堂其实有一个毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:08.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Wallhalla does have one problem
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个很吵的邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A noisy neighbor
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.67,0:17:14.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在墙外面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:14.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beyond these walls
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.51,0:17:18.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住着一只穿着吱吱叫鞋子的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:18.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there lives a creature with squeaky shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.22,0:17:21.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整天到处跺脚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:21.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who stomps around all day
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.35,0:17:25.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一只无时无刻欢欢乐乐尖叫的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:25.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A monster who shrieks with delight at all hours
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.35,0:17:28.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一只会发出刺耳尖笑的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:28.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A beast with an ear-piercing laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.94,0:17:34.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烦得让我都疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:34.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So annoying, it drove me mad
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,声音差不多是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it sounds like this
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.28,0:17:43.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我听过最难听的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:43.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the most horrible thing I've ever heard
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.33,0:17:46.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我真的好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:46.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure glad
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能跟你平平安安跟你在一块  沃利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to be safe in here with you, Wally
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.25,0:17:50.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:50.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.04,0:17:55.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能认识你就是我一生中最棒的一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:55.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Meeting ye has been the greatest day of me life
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是说现在晚上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or is it night time?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.01,0:17:59.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好几年前就没时间概念了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:59.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost track years ago
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.18,0:18:04.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想不想来参加交友宴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:04.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What say ye to a friendship feast?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd never ask
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.02,0:18:13.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为友情干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:13.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To friendship
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敬墙中殿堂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To Wallhalla
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.92,0:18:31.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,沃利  这是我吃过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:31.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wally, that was
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.88,0:18:34.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最具友情的一场盛宴了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:34.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the friendliest feast I ever had
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.55,0:18:35.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我跟小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:35.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess me and Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得去找回去的出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,better find our way back home
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.22,0:18:38.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:38.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.84,0:18:40.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:40.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是  我的宠物蜗牛小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, my pet snail Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.68,0:18:46.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的宠物蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:46.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your pet snail?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的宠物蜗牛才对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He be my pet snail
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且那也不叫小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And his name ain't Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.81,0:18:52.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而是小瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:52.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's "Garr-ee"
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.02,0:18:53.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:53.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:19:00.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1472,412)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.98,0:18:57.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:57.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Garr-ee"
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.86,0:19:00.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:00.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's funny
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那四处出没的笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That haunting laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was ye
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.50,0:19:13.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你烦得我都疯掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:13.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ye who drove me mad
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.01,0:19:24.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我诅咒你  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:24.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I curse thee, SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.26,0:19:26.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有你烦人的笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:26.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and thy irritating cackle
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.18,0:19:33.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要从你身上的洞拧出水来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:33.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm gonna wring the water from your pores
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.86,0:19:38.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚出墙中殿堂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:38.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be gone from Wallhalla
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.53,0:19:42.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在破坏我美丽的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:42.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are breaking me beautiful world
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're home?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你不马上出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you don't come out right now
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.70,0:19:50.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来不在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:50.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess not
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.75,0:19:54.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好  他家就是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:54.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, su casa es mi casa
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是葡萄干
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Raisins
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.56,0:20:12.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:12.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you don't
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.56,0:20:15.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:15.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, help us
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这片子好垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The show stinks
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.90,0:20:21.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:21.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boo
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.74,0:20:29.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快递到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:29.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The mail is here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是寄给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this isn't for me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.37,0:20:35.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就退还给寄件人好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:35.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just return to sender
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.83,0:20:36.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:36.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go down
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是寄给我的饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not-for-me cookies
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.68,0:20:49.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  谢天谢地你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:49.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, thank goodness you're here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.97,0:20:51.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能出去  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:51.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you mind, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.89,0:20:53.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还在用洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:53.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm using the bathroom
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.85,0:20:55.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:55.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.81,0:20:58.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我穿越了魔镜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:58.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm through the looking glass
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.19,0:21:00.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,墙中殿堂灭亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:00.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wallhalla has been destroyed
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.73,0:21:04.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们毁了我窄小又不适的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:04.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ye ruined me narrow, uncomfortable life
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.74,0:21:07.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那爱哭鬼是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:07.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's the cry baby?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.70,0:21:13.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外面的世界肯定会有你想念的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:11.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There has to be one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:13.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from the outside world that you miss
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.29,0:21:14.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:14.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.30,0:21:20.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:20.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.13,0:21:23.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是蟹黄堡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:23.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that the Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.26,0:21:27.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  我承认有我想念的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:27.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I admit there was one thing I missed
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.26,0:21:28.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我十几年来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:28.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've had to ration
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.89,0:21:32.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能限量吃这么一个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:32.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this one Krabby Patty for decades
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I have an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.73,0:21:43.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我妈的饼干怎么浮在马桶上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:43.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, why are my mom's cookies floating in the toilet?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.32,0:21:45.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该是忘记冲水了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:45.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I forgot to flush
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:50.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(618,440)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.41,0:21:57.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:21:57.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.71,0:22:00.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是应该说  下菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:22:00.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or should I say, order down
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.42,0:22:03.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:03.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank ye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:17.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(852,234)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.18,0:22:10.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有芥末酱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:10.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got any mustard?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.48,0:22:24.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是恨那笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:24.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I still hate that laugh
